Rip notes: Down Sampled Audio

Using one of 6 cute Fur Fighters battle your way through this awesome blend of FPS/Adventure/Platform/Puzzle game.

Hell bent on revenge, the Evil General Viggo has kidnapped members of your family. The strange collection of friends must blast & solve the puzzles to rescue thier siblings in this huge adventure.

Theres also multiplayer action supporting 2-4 players in the FluffMatch Mode.